 Kasese,
 Kyegegwa,
 Kiryandongo,
 and Masindi.
 Kasese and Kyegegwa are located in the southwestern corner of the study area near Lake George and border Kabarole district.
 Kiryandongo and Masindi lie in the northern part of the study area,
 at the northeastern tip of Lake Albert,
 adjacent to Hoima district.
 In these districts,
