\end_layout

\end_inset

 Similarly for aggregators,
 some aggregators that collect maize in control areas may actually ship to wholesalers that are supplying WFP,
 while aggregators located in areas where WFP procures may actually sell to a wholesaler that has now WFP link.
 Some of these limitations will be further addressed in a separate section by complementing the group-based comparisons with data on farmers’ and aggregators' actual transactions with WFP-linked buyers and using an instrumental variables regression framework (Section 
